{
  "stem": "8947.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my mother was very good in crafts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at one time, she was teaching crafts in Israel, when she was in Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I encouraged her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was teaching crafts at the women's club.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she always-- she wanted-- my mother was a very outgoing person, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- but then she helped my grandmother in the business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my father couldn't just stop her doing nothing in that sense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my first language-- and I carry this accent, which you hear today-- was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my parents, my grandparents, and my great grandparents were-- at that time when they were young, that whole territory, Transylvania, and this city of Cluj where most of my family was born, was a part of the Austro-Hungarian Empire.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents spoke well German, too, because of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Hungarian was my first language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that any language-- I speak other languages-- but the accent is definitely a Hungarian in all the languages that I mastered after that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Could you describe for me how some of the Jewish holidays were celebrated in your home?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you, just with the subject, I get very emotional.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I don't think that that I will ever see celebrations that we experience.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Forgive me, but this is a very weak point here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, you know, in the camps, when I was a prisoner, I had to-- I had to take my strengths and I took my strengths from the beautiful celebrations in our holidays.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the situation was terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never knew if I lived one day or another if I live at the end of the day and what's going to happen to me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I said to myself, well, I have to live.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have to make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
